---
title: Caribbean Pork Rissoles with Charred Corn & Sweet Chilli Slaw
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the pork rissoles in a
Caribbean jerk seasoning. It’s a dish that leaves a pleasant, warm feeling after you're done.
